ALAN SEALES: I guess Bruce--

00:29:33.700 --> 00:29:36.386
LAURIE METCALF: And quick ones
happening backstage, a lot

00:29:36.386 --> 00:29:38.082
of quick stuff back there.

00:29:38.082 --> 00:29:38.790
ALAN SEALES: Wow.

