So the rehearsals you
were talking about,

00:29:41.070 --> 00:29:41.990
how long were they?

00:29:41.990 --> 00:29:43.754
You said they were
six to seven weeks?

00:29:43.754 --> 00:29:44.420
WILL FREARS: No.

