00:30:13.760 --> 00:30:14.760
WILL FREARS: Oh, yeah.

00:30:14.760 --> 00:30:15.180
ALAN SEALES: Even afterwards?

00:30:15.180 --> 00:30:16.710
WILL FREARS: Not
opening, but close.

00:30:16.710 --> 00:30:17.570
ALAN SEALES: Yeah.

